1026
00:49:15,921 --> 00:49:17,590
Saya Yehezkiel Roswell.

1027
00:49:18,623 --> 00:49:19,707
Dan kami sudah menikah.

1028
00:49:39,371 --> 00:49:40,372
Wow!

1029
00:49:40,604 --> 00:49:42,272
Rumah siapa ini, Zeke?

1030
00:49:42,472 --> 00:49:43,957
Saya berhasil!

1031
00:49:43,981 --> 00:49:44,815
Saya berhasil!

1032
00:49:44,816 --> 00:49:49,720
Apakah saya benar-benar sudah menikah
kepada Tuan Yehezkiel Roswell?

1033
00:49:49,744 --> 00:49:51,640
Aduh, lucu sekali!

1034
00:49:51,664 --> 00:49:53,180
Anda ingin saya mencari kucing?

1035
00:49:53,204 --> 00:49:55,038
Apa kamu peduli, Lamperouge?

1036
00:49:55,039 --> 00:49:56,873
Selamat Hari Valentine, Moo!

1037
